#: ../../user/advanced-topics/secondary-storage.rst:13
#: 67e6fa59c68a4f398e8e007ff3297e03
msgid ""
"Suppose you have a fast but small primary SSD and a large but slow "
"secondary HDD. You may want to store a subset of your qubes on the HDD. "
"Or if you install a second SSD, you may want to use *that* for storage of"
" some qubes. This page explains how to use that second drive."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/secondary-storage.rst:16
